name: ALX Enterprise
overview:
Established in the year 2008, we, “ALX Enterprise”, are a renowned organization engaged in manufacturing a comprehensive assortment of Wire Drawing Dies ,PCD Dies,Rod Break Down Machine, Fine Wire Drawing Machine and Intermediate Wire Drawing Machine.

Our Team; Experienced professionals Quality controllers Sales & marketing executives Administrators

Infrastructure: We have established a state-of-the-art infrastructure, which is spread over a huge area and is facilitated with cutting-edge technology and hi-end tools and machines that enable us to offer an impeccable range of Wire Dies & Drawing Machines to our clients.

Quality Assurance: We are committed towards offering best quality Wire Dies & Drawing Machines to all our patrons. To manufacture these products, our professionals make use of high quality material procured from an authorized vendors of the market following the guidelines and standards laid by the industry.

Client Satisfaction: To meet the every expectation of our customers, we work hard in attaining maximum level of our customer satisfaction in order to offer them quality-assured Wire Dies & Drawing Machines to our prestigious clients.
